</p><p>Quaternions are used in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pur=
e_mathematics" title=3D"Pure mathematics">pure mathematics</a>, but also ha=
ve practical uses in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Applied_mathe=
matics" title=3D"Applied mathematics">applied mathematics</a>, particularly=
