er</a> group of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SO(3)" class=3D"mw=
-redirect" title=3D"SO(3)">SO(3)</a>. The positive and negative basis vecto=
rs form the eight-element <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quaterni=
on_group" title=3D"Quaternion group">quaternion group</a>.
</p>
