</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>A <i>quaternion</i> is an <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Expre=
ssion_(mathematics)" title=3D"Expression (mathematics)">expression</a> of t=
he form
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle a+b\,\mathbf {i} +c\,\mathbf {j} +d\,\mathbf {k} ,}">
