html mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">b</span>, <span class=3D"texhtml mv=
ar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">c</span>, <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" sty=
le=3D"font-style:italic;">d</span>  equals 1, the corresponding term is wri=
tten simply <span class=3D"texhtml"><b>i</b>, <b>j</b></span>, or <span cla=
ss=3D"texhtml"><b>k</b></span>.
</p><p>A quaternion <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline=
