</a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>Conjugation of quaternions is analogous to conjugation of complex number=
s and to transposition (also known as reversal) of elements of Clifford alg=
ebras. To define it, let <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-i=
nline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D=
"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=
=3D"{\displaystyle q=3Da+b\,\mathbf {i} +c\,\mathbf {j} +d\,\mathbf {k} }">
