on-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>Just as complex numbers can be <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/=
Matrix_representation_of_complex_numbers" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Ma=
trix representation of complex numbers">represented as matrices</a>, so can=
