mple, setting <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>c</i> =3D <i>d</i> =3D 0</span> pr=
oduces a diagonal complex matrix representation of complex numbers, and set=
ting <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>b</i> =3D <i>d</i> =3D 0</span> produces a =
real matrix representation.</li>
<li>The norm of a quaternion (the square root of the product with its conju=
gate, as with complex numbers) is the square root of the <a href=3D"https:/=
/en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Determinant" title=3D"Determinant">determinant</a> o=
